## Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph AutoPipeline["core/auto_pipeline.py"]
        P1["Phase 1: Download<br/>(parallel: video+thumb+transcript)"]
        P2["Phase 2: Split<br/>(sequential: split→verify→punctuate→save)"]
    end
    
    subgraph Tab["ui/auto_pipeline_tab.py"]
        UI["UI: URLs + Config"]
        P3["Phase 3: Rewrite<br/>(delegates to RewriteStyleTab)"]
    end
    
    UI --> P1 --> P2 --> P3
```

**Key design decision:** Phase 3 (Rewrite) delegates to `RewriteStyleTab._do_renew_review()` / [_do_renew_style()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/rewrite_style_tab.py#2056-2559) rather than duplicating 1500+ lines of rewrite pipeline code. Config is synchronized via [_sync_config_to_rewrite_tab()](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/auto_pipeline_tab.py#1013-1060).

## Function Reuse

All pipeline logic reuses existing functions — zero code duplication:
- `yt_downloader`: [get_video_info](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#489-545), [get_transcript_ytdlp](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#1061-1169), [download_video](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#768-862), [download_thumbnail_file](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#864-952), [extract_timestamps](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#572-613), [build_transcript_file](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/yt_downloader.py#615-649)
- `chapter_splitter`: [classify_script_type](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#150-187), [split_chapters](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#552-735), [verify_chapters](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#737-785), [punctuate_chapters](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#787-884), [save_chapters](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#894-940), [merge_chapters](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#942-968), [save_summary](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/chapter_splitter.py#970-1041)
